cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.NA, cs.DS, cs.SY 

This paper deals with robust parameter estimation in computer vision, which is a common problem in the field of computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes an iteratively reweighted algorithm for solving the maximum consensus problem, which involves optimization techniques. This suggests that the paper could also be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.NA (Numerical Analysis). Additionally, the paper involves the use of algorithms and data structures, which could place it under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, the paper also deals with control systems, which could place it under cs.SY (Systems and Control).
